These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, firefighter, fisherman, designer
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the firefighter##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the photographer##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the firefighter is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Job      | fisherman  | firefighter | designer        | photographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
House: craftsman, art-deco, modern, tower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the modern house##7
2. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
3. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| House     | modern | art-deco       | tower         | craftsman     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, skiing, ice-hockey, weightlifting
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is swimming##7
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | swimming  | weightlifting   | skiing |

