.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian, malaysian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the nigerian and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the turkish##1
4. the malaysian is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | japanese   | malaysian | turkish  |

