.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, metal, disco, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, chinese, german
1. the german is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the american is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the german is somewhere between the fan of metal and the fan of funk##7
5. the german is on the left of the chinese##1
6. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5
7. the fan of metal is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | disco | funk   | d&b | metal |
| Nationality   | american      | brazilian | german      | chinese |

