2. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to berlin##7
7. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| City   | colone    | venice | berlin   | nizza |

