.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, crime, sports, family
1. the argentine is not the person watching family movies##6
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
3. the spanish is the person watching sports movies##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Movie-Genre           | sports   | family    | disaster       | crime  |

