.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, dunhill, siglo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, skiing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
2. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the siglo-smoker##6
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the pall-mall-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | old-henry | dunhill | siglo |
| Sport   | tennis  | sailing    | climbing    | skiing  |

