.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, water
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, canadian, egyptian
1. the indian is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is somewhere between the person drinking water and the canadian##7
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the canadian is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the canadian##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | cola   | mirinda | fanta | water   |
| Nationality   | indonesian | canadian   | egyptian | indian |

