4. the person traveling to venice is somewhere between the person traveling to san-francisco and the fan of metal##7
5. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person traveling to london##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
